  "title": "Senior Researcher - ESG / Carbon Capture / Sustainable Finance (Permanent)",
  "description": "<p>The Researcher / Senior Researcher will be responsible for conducting research on<strong> customer challenge, creating advanced technology/solution and business mode</strong>l, related to <strong>Carbon Capture and Storage.</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Conduct research activities and develop advanced technology/solution for carbon capture and storage, including assessment, modelling, and prediction.</li><li>Create service design and business model.</li><li>Conduct Proof of Concept (PoC) to demonstrate solution value with real world application.</li><li>Conduct activities in customer engagement, requirement study and solution proposal.</li><li>Create proposal documents, presentation material, and technical report.</li><li>Collaborate with global research teams and various parties to develop and deliver solution.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Master's Degree or PhD</li><li>Computer Engineering, Geological Analytics, Environmental Science</li><li>Min 3 years of relevant working experiences in <strong>carbon capture and storage, such as assessment, modelling, and prediction</strong></li><li>Working experience in service design and customer facing activities</li><li>Good hands-on capability in Geological Analysis, Digital MRV, Blockchain</li><li>Knowledge of Carbon Capture and Storage</li><li>Design Thinking</li></ul>",
